description:
BlockEquity is a premium ENS holder & web3 developer wanting to develop and build out decentralized domain names in a wide variety of industries and verticals. In addition to the premium ENS domains currently in possession, the goal of BlockEquity DAO will be to register and purchase expired names & premium names from the secondary market with the goal of developing these prime assets into passive revenue generating businesses of their own brand identity and sustainability.

DAO Funds will be used to:
- Develop premium ENS domains into passive income assets.
- Hire world-class talent from the Developer_DAO
- Ideate & Vote on which software ideas to develop on premium land.
- Come check out the Discord for more details and vibes.
payDisclosure: You acknowledge that this is an experiment in decentralized coordination and does not constitute a financial investment.
